rows.label: tlk70000077_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey there!
You're pretty famous these days!

rows.label: tlk70000077_04_msg0002
rows.name:
I'll be honest, I never thought the
people who brought me all that terrible
food, would get to where you are now!

rows.label: tlk70000077_04_msg0003
rows.name:
I still can't quite believe there was
one of you fine folk who could cook
like that...

rows.label: tlk70000077_04_msg0004
rows.name:
That cooking just oozed the personality
of the person who made it.

rows.label: tlk70000077_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Call it rough, call it rude,
call it brutal...

rows.label: tlk70000077_04_msg0006
rows.name:
Huh? What's up with that blonde lass?
She's gone as red as a beetroot!
